Adriana Chechik just revealed she was pregnant when she got injured at Twitchcon. She jumped into that foam pit earlier this month and broke her back in two places. But during a stream over the weekend said she couldn’t keep the pregnancy because of the surgeries she had to undergo. So now, people are not just heartbroken for her, but also hoping she is lining up a massive lawsuit.
